snippet.title: Super Bitsy Land (Bitsy game) playthrough
snippet.description:
Link: https://pocketfruit.itch.io/super-bitsy-land

Here is a playthrough of the Bitsy Game 'Super Bitsy Land' - a Gameboy like short pseudo-platformer I would say. I always loooooved the Gameboy Mario and Wario games the most somehow.
